org.apache.plc4x.java.ads.api.generic

Interface AdsData

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ByteBufSupplier, ByteReadable, LengthSupplier, Serializable
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface AdsData
extends ByteReadable
    ADS Data n bytes The ADS data range contains the parameter of the single ADS commands. The structure of the data array depends on the ADS command. Some ADS commands require no additional data.
